  <brief_title>The Mininimum Effective Anaesthetic Volume of Local Anaesthetic in Ultrasound-guided &quot;Shamrock&quot; Lumbar Plexus Block</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Mininimum Effective Anaesthetic Volume of Local Anaesthetic in Ultrasound-guided &quot;Shamrock&quot; Lumbar Plexus Block</official_title>
